history.content: I'm a rising CS-intended sophomore and was planning on taking 61C, 70, and Anthro 2AC this fall. I know I need to phase 1 70 for optimal discussion times, but does anyone have any advice on which of 61C and Anthro 2AC to phase 1? In other words, Is 61C going to expand to fit everyone in and does it matter what lab and discussion time you have or can you show up to any of them (as we did in 61A and 61B)? Or would it be recommended to phase 1 the class?
